  <h1>BMI and <em>Calorie Calculator</em><br>— How They Work Together</h1>
  <p>BMI tells you where you are. A calorie calculator tells you what to eat to get where you want to be. Here's how to use both together.</p>
</div>

<div style="font-size:.8rem;color:var(--ink3);margin:0 auto 24px;max-width:720px;padding:0 20px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">Reviewed by <strong>Sarah Mitchell, BSc Nutrition</strong> · Last updated: <strong>July 2026</strong></div>

